				</ukm:Metadata><Secondary><Schedules RestrictExtent="S" RestrictStartDate="2026-04-01"><Schedule DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2021/249/schedule/2" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2021/249/schedule/2" NumberOfProvisions="4" id="schedule-2" RestrictExtent="S" RestrictStartDate="2026-04-01"><Number>SCHEDULE 2</Number><TitleBlock>
<Title>Amount of second adult rebate</Title>
</TitleBlock><ScheduleBody><P1 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2021/249/schedule/2/paragraph/1" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2021/249/schedule/2/paragraph/1" id="schedule-2-paragraph-1" RestrictExtent="S" RestrictStartDate="2026-04-01"><Pnumber><CommentaryRef Ref="key-a1"/>1</Pnumber><P1para><Text>Subject to paragraphs 2 and 3, the second adult rebate in respect of a day for the purpose of regulation 91 is to be determined in accordance with the following table.</Text><Tabular Orientation="portrait"><xhtml:table xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" cols="2"><xhtml:colgroup><xhtml:col width="213.2pt"/><xhtml:col width="213.2pt"/></xhtml:colgroup><xhtml:thead><xhtml:tr><xhtml:th xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" rowspan="1" colspan="1" fo:border-top-style="solid" fo:border-top-width="0.5pt" fo:border-top-color="black" fo:border-bottom-style="solid" fo:border-bottom-width="0.5pt" fo:border-bottom-color="black"><Para><Text><Emphasis>(1)</Emphasis></Text></Para><Para><Text><Emphasis>Second adult</Emphasis></Text></Para></xhtml:th><xhtml:th xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" rowspan="1" colspan="1" fo:border-top-style="solid" fo:border-top-width="0.5pt" fo:border-top-color="black" fo:border-bottom-style="solid" fo:border-bottom-width="0.5pt" fo:border-bottom-color="black"><Para><Text><Emphasis>(2)</Emphasis></Text></Para><Para><Text><Emphasis>Second adult rebate</Emphasis></Text></Para></xhtml:th></xhtml:tr></xhtml:thead><xhtml:tbody><xhtml:tr><xhtml:td rowspan="1" colspan="1"><OrderedList Decoration="parens" Type="alpha"><ListItem><Para><Text>Where the second adult or all second adults are in receipt of a qualifying income-related benefit or state pension credit,</Text></Para></ListItem></OrderedList></xhtml:td><xhtml:td rowspan="1" colspan="1">25 per cent of the council tax due in respect of that day,</xhtml:td></xhtml:tr><xhtml:tr><xhtml:td rowspan="1" colspan="1"><OrderedList Decoration="parens" Type="alpha" Start="2"><ListItem><Para><Text>where the gross income of the second adult or, where there is more than one second adult, their aggregate gross income disregarding any income of persons on a qualifying income-related benefit <Addition ChangeId="key-a2" CommentaryRef="key-a2">, universal credit with no earned income,</Addition>  or state pension credit—</Text></Para></ListItem></OrderedList></xhtml:td><xhtml:td rowspan="1" colspan="1"/></xhtml:tr><xhtml:tr><xhtml:td rowspan="1" colspan="1"><OrderedList Decoration="parens" Type="roman"><ListItem><Para><Text>is less than <Substitution ChangeId="key-a3" CommentaryRef="key-a3">£282.00</Substitution> per week,</Text></Para></ListItem></OrderedList></xhtml:td><xhtml:td rowspan="1" colspan="1">15 per cent of the council tax due in respect of that day,</xhtml:td></xhtml:tr><xhtml:tr><xhtml:td rowspan="1" colspan="1"><OrderedList Decoration="parens" Type="roman" Start="2"><ListItem><Para><Text>is not less than <Substitution ChangeId="key-a4" CommentaryRef="key-a4">£282.00</Substitution> per week but is less than <Substitution ChangeId="key-a5" CommentaryRef="key-a5">£383.00</Substitution> per week,</Text></Para></ListItem></OrderedList></xhtml:td><xhtml:td rowspan="1" colspan="1">7.5 per cent of the council tax due in respect of that day,</xhtml:td></xhtml:tr><xhtml:tr><xhtml:td rowspan="1" colspan="1"><OrderedList Decoration="parens" Type="alpha" Start="3"><ListItem><Para><Text>where the second adult or all second adults are in receipt of universal credit and have no earned income</Text></Para></ListItem></OrderedList></xhtml:td><xhtml:td rowspan="1" colspan="1">25 per cent of the council tax due in respect of that day,</xhtml:td></xhtml:tr><xhtml:tr><xhtml:td xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" rowspan="1" colspan="1" fo:border-bottom-style="solid" fo:border-bottom-width="0.5pt" fo:border-bottom-color="black"><OrderedList Decoration="parens" Type="alpha" Start="4"><ListItem><Para><Text> <Substitution ChangeId="key-a6" CommentaryRef="key-a6">where the dwelling would be wholly occupied by a person to whom regulation 20(2) (students) applies but for the presence of one or more second adults who are in receipt of— </Substitution></Text><OrderedList Decoration="parens" Type="roman"><ListItem><Para><Text><Substitution ChangeId="key-a6" CommentaryRef="key-a6">a qualifying income-related benefit or state pension credit, or</Substitution></Text></Para></ListItem><ListItem><Para><Text><Substitution ChangeId="key-a6" CommentaryRef="key-a6">universal credit and have no earned income.</Substitution></Text></Para></ListItem></OrderedList></Para></ListItem></OrderedList></xhtml:td><xhtml:td xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" rowspan="1" colspan="1" fo:border-bottom-style="solid" fo:border-bottom-width="0.5pt" fo:border-bottom-color="black">100 per cent of the council tax due in respect of that day.</xhtml:td></xhtml:tr></xhtml:tbody></xhtml:table></Tabular></P1para></P1></ScheduleBody></Schedule></Schedules></Secondary><Commentaries><Commentary id="key-a2" Type="F"><Para><Text>Words in sch. 2 para. 1 Table inserted (31.3.2022) by virtue of <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2022/52" id="d9e5" Class="ScottishStatutoryInstrument" Year="2022" Number="52" Title="The Council Tax Reduction (Scotland) Amendment Regulations 2022">The Council Tax Reduction (Scotland) Amendment Regulations 2022 (S.S.I. 2022/52)</Citation>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="d9e5" id="cc190597001419" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2022/52/regulation/1/2" SectionRef="regulation-1-2">regs. 1(2)</CitationSubRef>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="d9e5" id="cc131095151787" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2022/52/regulation/19/a/i" Operative="true" SectionRef="regulation-19-a-i">19(a)(i)</CitationSubRef></Text></Para></Commentary><Commentary id="key-a6" Type="F"><Para><Text>Words in <CitationSubRef id="ccd8e2202305231616085770100" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2021/249/schedule/2/paragraph/1" SectionRef="schedule-2-paragraph-1">sch. 2 para. 1</CitationSubRef> table substituted (31.3.2022) by <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2022/52" id="d10e5" Class="ScottishStatutoryInstrument" Year="2022" Number="52" Title="The Council Tax Reduction (Scotland) Amendment Regulations 2022">The Council Tax Reduction (Scotland) Amendment Regulations 2022 (S.S.I. 2022/52)</Citation>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="d10e5" id="ccd8e8202305231616085770100" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2022/52/regulation/1/2" SectionRef="regulation-1-2">regs. 1(2)</CitationSubRef>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="d10e5" id="ccd8e11202305231616085770100" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2022/52/regulation/19/a/ii" Operative="true" SectionRef="regulation-19-a-ii">19(a)(ii)</CitationSubRef></Text></Para></Commentary><Commentary id="key-a1" Type="I"><Para><Text><CitationSubRef id="cnh7oncs4-00596" SectionRef="schedule-2-paragraph-1" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2021/249/schedule/2/paragraph/1">Sch. 2 para. 1</CitationSubRef> in force at 1.4.2022, see <CitationSubRef id="cnh7oncs4-00597" CitationRef="" SectionRef="regulation-1" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2021/249/regulation/1" Operative="true">reg. 1</CitationSubRef></Text></Para></Commentary><Commentary id="key-a3" Type="F"><Para><Text>Sum in <CitationSubRef id="c6gaah8h6-00007" SectionRef="schedule-2-paragraph-1" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2021/249/schedule/2/paragraph/1">sch. 2 para. 1</CitationSubRef> Table  substituted (1.4.2026) by <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2026/56" id="c6gaah8h6-00008" Class="ScottishStatutoryInstrument" Year="2026" Number="56" Title="The Council Tax Reduction (Miscellaneous Amendment) (Scotland) Regulations 2026">The Council Tax Reduction (Miscellaneous Amendment) (Scotland) Regulations 2026 (S.S.I. 2026/56)</Citation>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="c6gaah8h6-00008" id="c6gaah8h6-00009" SectionRef="regulation-1" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2026/56/regulation/1">regs. 1</CitationSubRef>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="c6gaah8h6-00008" id="c6gaah8h6-00010" SectionRef="regulation-15-a" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2026/56/regulation/15/a" Operative="true">15(a)</CitationSubRef></Text></Para></Commentary><Commentary id="key-a4" Type="F"><Para><Text>Sum in <CitationSubRef id="c6gaah8h6-00017" SectionRef="schedule-2-paragraph-1" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2021/249/schedule/2/paragraph/1">sch. 2 para. 1</CitationSubRef> Table  substituted (1.4.2026) by <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2026/56" id="c6gaah8h6-00018" Class="ScottishStatutoryInstrument" Year="2026" Number="56" Title="The Council Tax Reduction (Miscellaneous Amendment) (Scotland) Regulations 2026">The Council Tax Reduction (Miscellaneous Amendment) (Scotland) Regulations 2026 (S.S.I. 2026/56)</Citation>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="c6gaah8h6-00018" id="c6gaah8h6-00019" SectionRef="regulation-1" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2026/56/regulation/1">regs. 1</CitationSubRef>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="c6gaah8h6-00018" id="c6gaah8h6-00020" SectionRef="regulation-15-b-i" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2026/56/regulation/15/b/i" Operative="true">15(b)(i)</CitationSubRef></Text></Para></Commentary><Commentary id="key-a5" Type="F"><Para><Text>Sum in <CitationSubRef id="c6gaah8h6-00027" SectionRef="schedule-2-paragraph-1" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2021/249/schedule/2/paragraph/1">sch. 2 para. 1</CitationSubRef> Table  substituted (1.4.2026) by <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2026/56" id="c6gaah8h6-00028" Class="ScottishStatutoryInstrument" Year="2026" Number="56" Title="The Council Tax Reduction (Miscellaneous Amendment) (Scotland) Regulations 2026">The Council Tax Reduction (Miscellaneous Amendment) (Scotland) Regulations 2026 (S.S.I. 2026/56)</Citation>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="c6gaah8h6-00028" id="c6gaah8h6-00029" SectionRef="regulation-1" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2026/56/regulation/1">regs. 1</CitationSubRef>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="c6gaah8h6-00028" id="c6gaah8h6-00030" SectionRef="regulation-15-b-ii" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2026/56/regulation/15/b/ii" Operative="true">15(b)(ii)</CitationSubRef></Text></Para></Commentary></Commentaries></Legislation>